{"tid":2163803,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 落實 HK$4,055 億收購 ARM    預計夏季尾完成交易","createTime":"2020-08-19T01:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T10:30:15.000Z","uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03975e0bb3072c611f251055d9d82ea34fe5698c","tid":2163803,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"SoftBank 創辦人兼社長孫正義早前證實正積極考慮於近期將 2016 年收購的 ARM 對外出售，而近年發展順利的 NVIDIA 可能為目前 ARM 最大的潛在買家。最新消息指，交易已進入倒數階段，並可能會在今年夏季完成，交易金額可望高達 400 億英鎊（約港幣 HK$4,055 億）。<br />\n <br />\n據英媒《Evening Standard》報導， SoftBank 與 NVIDIA 就 ARM 交易已進入最後談判階段，預計持續 30 至 45 天後可達共識，即最快將在月底完成交易，外界估計 NVIDIA 出價高達 400 億英鎊（約港幣 HK$4,055 億）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/18/nvidia-arm/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F18%2Fnvidia-arm%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5nfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=cf093554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/18/nvidia-arm/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"79e3ff5685cb8d69092e93cb9101a2fbc22760ce","tid":2163803,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"又落實 又最後談判階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2838e209d127b9de12b21f69e4d5702d132ab9","tid":2163803,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"ARM變咗美資<br />\n即係華為就算搵到CPU代工廠都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連ARM架構本身都唔用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef689503c942aab7dae74830af9e66e808d42f5","tid":2163803,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be2838e209d127b9de12b21f69e4d5702d132ab9","tid":2163803,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"ARM變咗美資<br />\n即係華為就算搵到CPU代工廠都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 